&lt;li&gt;Ensures the leadership team is kept informed of study progress and that all critical issues are appropriately escalated within the organization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fosters a close partnership with CMO and Medical Affairs team on all studies, from study design, site selection to KOL partnerships and BD Due Diligence.&lt;/li&gt;
