&lt;li&gt;Key Partner to BD in all due diligence for clinical assessment and development pathways along with appropriate risk assessment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exhibits and fosters key leadership competencies, including an innovative mindset, strong business acumen, an outcome-driven orientation, and a commitment to growing and expanding the capabilities and capacity of the team&lt;/li&gt;
